==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Citrine
<hw>Cit"rine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>citrin</ets>. See <er>Citron</er>.]</ety> <def>Like a citron or
lemon; of a lemon color; greenish yellow.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Citrine ointment</b></col> <fld>(Med.)</fld>, <cd>a
yellowish mercurial ointment, the <altname>unguentum hydrargyri
nitratis</altname>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Citrine</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Citrine
<hw>Cit"rine</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A yellow, pellucid variety of
quartz.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Citron</ent>⟦br⟧
